    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p><i>7th-level Drakewarden feature</i></p><p>The bond you share with your drake intensifies, protecting you and stoking the drake's fury. When you summon your drake, it grows wings on its back and gains a flying speed equal to its walking speed.</p><p>In addition, while your drake is summoned, you and the drake gain the following benefits:</p><ul class=\"rd__list rd__list-hang-notitle\"><li class=\"rd__li \"><p class=\"rd__p-list-item\" data-roll-name-ancestor=\"Drake Mount\"><span class=\"bold rd__list-item-name\">Drake Mount.</span> The drake grows to Medium size. Reflecting your special bond, you can use the drake as a mount if your size is Medium or smaller. While you are riding your drake, it can't use the flying speed of this feature.</p></li><li class=\"rd__li \"><p class=\"rd__p-list-item\" data-roll-name-ancestor=\"Magic Fang\"><span class=\"bold rd__list-item-name\">Magic Fang.</span> The drake's Bite attack deals an extra [[/damage 1d6]] damage of the type chosen for the drake's Draconic Essence.</p></li><li class=\"rd__li \"><p class=\"rd__p-list-item\" data-roll-name-ancestor=\"Resistance\"><span class=\"bold rd__list-item-name\">Resistance.</span> You gain resistance to the damage type chosen for the drake's Draconic Essence.</p></li></ul></div>",
      "chat": ""
    },
